title: Population of the Netherlands 2019 , by age
summary: Overall Number of inhabitants has decreased over the Year.
Number of inhabitants is roughly constant from 0_-_20_years to 20_-_40_years, and finally slightly decreasing from 20_-_40_years to 65_-_80_years.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 40_-_65_years and 65_-_80_years.
Maximum Number of inhabitants, about 5866334.0 was reported at Year 40_-_65_years
Minimum Number of inhabitants about 2515184.0 was reached at Year 65_-_80_years
